comments: Mills (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Curry (GSW) and absorbs the contact.
Toscano-Anderson's (GSW) momentum carries him forward into Gay (SAS) and he makes lower body contact with Gay as he returns to the floor during his jump shot attempt.
Delay of game violation is correctly called on the Warriors.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Murray (SAS) and makes marginal contact during the screen.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Gay (SAS) and does not dislodge him during the pick.
Curry (GSW) draws Gay (SAS) into the air towards him and the contact results in a foul on Gay (SAS) even if contact is initiated by Curry (GSW).
Green (GSW) absorbs the body contact from DeRozan (SAS) as he contests his driving shot attempt at the basket.
Mills (SAS) makes contact with Green's (GSW) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Green (GSW) makes incidental contact to Murray's (SAS) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
White (SAS) makes incidental contact to Curry's (GSW) hand after the release of his driving shot attempt.
DeRozan (SAS) slightly veers into Oubre Jr.'s (GSW) path at the end of his drive and the contact is marginal.
Gay (SAS) makes inadvertent contact to the ball as it goes off his foot during his dribble.
Curry (GSW) makes marginal contact to White's (SAS) body at the end of his drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Curry (GSW) and White (SAS) briefly engage and disengage during the inbounds.
Oubre Jr. (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Murray (SAS) and absorbs the contact.
White (SAS) makes incidental contact to Curry's (GSW) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) commits a take foul on DeRozan (SAS).
White (SAS) places his hand on Green's (GSW) arm and immediately removes it at the start of Green's upward shooting motion.
Lee (GSW) commits a take foul on DeRozan (SAS).
